# spectre — exclude binary and sensitive engagement artefacts
# Documentation (Markdown) is the only content tracked in this repository.

# Raw evidence archives and captures
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.cap

# Tool output dumps and scan artefacts
*.nmap
*.gnmap
*.xml
*.html
!docs/*.html
nikto.*
gobuster.txt
whatweb.txt
linpeas_out.txt
*_session.log
*.log

# Screenshots / images (evidence captures held offline)
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.pdf

# Integrity manifests referencing offline evidence
evidence.sha256
*.sha256

# Credentials, keys, host data
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
id_*
*_rsa
*_ed25519
.env
secrets*

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# Build-instruction file — keep local, never publish
CLAUDE.md
